sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant RASA as Rasa Server
    participant NLU as NLU Pipeline
    participant PHO as PhoBERTIntentClassifier
    participant FB as FallbackClassifier
    participant TR as Tracker
    participant CORE as Rasa Core
    participant NLG as Domain NLG
    participant ACT as Action Server
    participant RAG as LightRAG

    U->>RASA: Gui message text
    RASA->>NLU: parse(message)
    NLU->>PHO: Tien xu ly + VnCoreNLP + PhoBERT predict
    PHO-->>NLU: intent, confidence, intent_ranking
    NLU->>NLU: RegexEntityExtractor + EntitySynonymMapper
    NLU->>FB: Kiem tra threshold 0.65 va ambiguity 0.05
    alt Confidence thap hoac gan nhau
        FB-->>NLU: intent = nlu_fallback
    else Du tin cay
        FB-->>NLU: Giu intent du doan
    end
    NLU-->>RASA: parse_data
    RASA->>TR: Cap nhat latest_message, slots, events
    RASA->>CORE: Du doan next action bang RulePolicy/MemoizationPolicy
    alt Action la utter_*
        CORE->>NLG: Lay response template tu domain.yml
        NLG-->>RASA: text/buttons
    else Custom action
        CORE->>ACT: run(action, tracker, domain)
        alt Fallback hoac can tra cuu tri thuc
            ACT->>RAG: Query theo cau hoi va ngu canh
            RAG-->>ACT: Cau tra loi / references
        end
        ACT-->>RASA: events + response
    end
    RASA->>TR: Ghi bot events
    RASA-->>U: Tra response payload
